      "content": "but i already started doing it... i stopped the warfarin three days ago and i've been taking the garlic every morning plus a big spinach shake. i feel fine so far, no bruising or anything. if i just keep doing this and maybe add some ginger root to the smoothies, is that enough to keep my risk low without needing to go back to the clinic? i just dont want to be told i have to go back on the pills.",
